'''Ruth Ndulu Maingi''' (yavutse 22 Gicurasi 1983), ni umukinnyi wa filime wo [[Kenya|muri Kenya]] . <ref>https://www.kenyans.co.ke/news/54762-ruth-maingi-ex-ktn-actor-who-was-conned-twice-house-hunting-video</ref> Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime  ''[[18 Hours|18 hours]]'',''The Distant Boat'' na ''Midlife Crisis''<ref>https://frankensaurus.com/18_Hours</ref> .

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 22 Gicurasi 1983 i Machakos, muri Kenya nk'uwa kane mu muryango hamwe na bavandimwe be batandatu. <ref name="SPLA">http://kenya.spla.pro/en/file.person.ruth-ndulu-maingi-salome.42819.html</ref> Yize mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Kathiani na Township School Primary School i Machakos . Yarangije impamyabumenyi mu bwishingizi nyuma y'amashuri yisumbuye. <ref name="standardmedia">https://www.standardmedia.co.ke/evewoman/amp/article/2000121454/fashion-forward-actress</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye umwuga we wo kubyina. Ariko, nyuma yaje kwimukira mu buhanzi kugira ngo akore umwuga maze yinjira mu ishuri ry’imyidagaduro ry’igihugu cya [[Kenya]] imyaka ibiri. Muri 2007, yinjiye mu bitaramo bya Kigezi Ndoto. Hanyuma muri 2008, yimukiye mu Buhinde ''akinira'' ''Sauti Kimya'' na Githaa. 

Muri 2011 yakinnye bwa mbere muri firime na ''Marshal yo muri Finlande'' <ref>https://thecitizenng.com/kenyan-actress-ndulu-maingi-makes-nollywood-debut/</ref>. Muri uwo mwaka, yatoranijwe kugira ngo ayobore muri televiziyo ''Lies that Bind'', byatangiye kuri televiziyo. Muri uruhererekane, yakinnye 'Salome', umugore wa gatatu n'urukundo nyarwo rwa Richard Juma, n'umugore wa gatatu<ref>https://www.wordaz.com/Maingi.html</ref>. Noneho muri 2013, yakinnye mu ikinamico izwi cyane ya Swahili ''Mama Duka'' afite uruhare runini<ref>https://peoplepill.com/people/ruth-maingi</ref>.  Ku ruhare rwe, yaje guhabwa icyubahiro muri 2014 Magic Magic Viewers Choice Awards 2014 . 

Yagize uruhare runini nk'umutoza muri serivise ya tereviziyo ''The Team'', hamwe na Media Focus kuri Afrika yakozwe na Dreamcatcher<ref>https://ng.opera.news/ng/en/entertainment/c6f54332d15718eb80f076450095f8be

</ref>. Muri 2014, yakinnye muri firime ebyiri: ''The Next African Film Maker'' na ''Orphan'' .  Muri 2018, yakinnye bwa mbere muri Nollywood muri firime ''Family First'' iyobowe na Lancelot Imasuen<ref>https://www.vanguardngr.com/2018/09/kenyan-actress-ndulu-maingi-gets-her-nollywood-calling/</ref> . <ref>https://thecitizenng.com/kenyan-actress-ndulu-maingi-makes-nollywood-debut/</ref>

